Output1: Ls174T-pTER-β-catenin cells carry a doxycyclin-inducible shRNA against β-catenin. Cells were left untreated (con) or shRNA was induced for 72 hours with doxycycline (dox). Total RNA was isolated and analyzed on Affymetrix U133 Plus 2.0 to generate expression profiles.

Ls174T-L8 cells carry a doxycyclin-inducible dominant-negative Tcf4 transgene. Cells were untreated (con) or trangene expression was induced for 24 hours with doxycycline (dox). Total RNA was isolated and analyzed on Affymetrix U133 Plus 2.0 to generate expression profiles.
